{"tid":1271142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四大訴求中 最重要其實都係 獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-01T05:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T06:59:23.000Z","uid":17008,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ea924bbd46531b5c61b957ee8b6b1174410f6ea3","tid":1271142,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"樣樣都緊要 <br />\n林鄭換走下個唔會好幾多 反而林鄭已經極低民望 次次出黎又串又喊 搞到仲多人示威 係好事<br />\n<br />\n暫緩再重啟機會好低 就算係 只要佢一反口急推 出黎既人會更多更暴力<br />\n<br />\n撤暴動定性 放人 依個的確好重要 但因為暴動罪入罪門檻高 如果搵唔到片 其他證據都唔易入<br />\n<br />\n但唔夠獨立調查委員會重要 只要一成立到  <br />\n好多警察要坐監 問責 停職 <br />\n打後既所有示威都再惡唔出樣 <br />\n而且又大量片段影到曬用過份暴力 成立獨立調查委員會更有理有據<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要推一個 依個應該排第一？"},{"pid":"e56273f94f3a95d23ff30f7482dd2ac45b550f3d","tid":1271142,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:36:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a45266059d9a9d21f28dc24b2800d89ed26a02f9","tid":1271142,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abf93ae13c6398d8fc752e694225e476cb1352c7","tid":1271142,"uid":51872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e756e952451394bae6a5e6fa85467f5f9cb5cc","tid":1271142,"uid":174676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4c08a28e3828f34515aab08bcc8dddb05a9c5b4","tid":1271142,"uid":38761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n如果真係做到真正獨立嘅，唔係又好似禮頓單野一樣，不了了之！"},{"pid":"2163f0398ca61aba005d7973b5aa420a688601a1","tid":1271142,"uid":76347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"推呀 坐係屋企既麻煩都幫下手啦"},{"pid":"a66f893faefd9d5d2d7f8a280ea2954e2511b282","tid":1271142,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><